These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
City: berlin, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, gospel
1. the fan of techno is in an even position##4
2. the fan of gospel is the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| City   | marseilles | berlin |
| Music-Genre     | gospel    | techno   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, australian
1. the turkish is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Flower   | rose | daffodil        |
| Nationality      | turkish  | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, april
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, ebony
1. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | april    | july |
| Color   | white | ebony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
City: san-francisco, berlin
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, surfing
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| City   | san-francisco      | berlin |
| Sport       | skateboarding | surfing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog
House: colonial, wooden
1. the colonial house is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Pet           | ferret | hedgehog |
| House   | wooden    | colonial         |

 #################################

 
