.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, garlic
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta
1. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Food   | garlic | papaya   |
| Beverage         | sprite | fanta |

